works.description: After all the baselworld wrist beauties, you will find this diamond-encrusted iPod nano watch by ZShock, shocking like its namesake. The embellished version is dished out to seduce the rich Apple fanboys, who are constantly on a lookout for the pimped out Apple gadgets to satiate their need for bling. The company is also offering to customize the iPod watch to suit your taste. Though we loved their custom G-shock collection with dazzling bezels along with their collection of limited edition watches for the rich nerds
